  "display_name": "Figma MCP",
  "description": "Figma MCP workflow skill. Use this skill when the user needs Use the Figma MCP server to fetch design context, screenshots, variables, and assets from Figma, and to translate Figma nodes into production code. Use when a task involves Figma URLs, node IDs, design-to-code implementation, or Figma MCP setup and troubleshooting. Covers general Figma data fetching and exploration. Do NOT use when the goal is specifically pixel-perfect code implementation from a Figma design (use figma-implement-design instead) and the operator should rely on the packaged workflow, support pack, troubleshooting notes, and provenance links before merging or handing off.",
